creator: Narcissus Games
descriptionHtml: Bouncy Panda is a simple chill game which is all about hand control. As the points go up so does the speed of the panda meaning it will require less tilt input as the score gets higher. The game also has a leaderboard which displays the top 15 scores worldwide. In order to get your score added to the leaderboard you must set a name in the settings page. This game was created using the Godot engine and uses Silentwolf for its leaderboard services. Compete with friends as well as with others for a spot in the top 15 world wide. Good luck and have fun.
descriptionShort: Tilt your phone to move the panda and score points by bouncing off the platforms
